name: Princess Jane
description: I am calm, romantic, well-balanced, family oriented. It is very hard to tell about myself, but I will try to do it, because I want you know more about me. By nature I am humorist person and during all my life I am optimist. I always try to reach my goal anyway for I life here?:) I have a big and beautiful eyes and I prefer to look at persons eyes when I talk with him. I am very simple person and I try to tell what I think. I do not like to save my thoughts in my mind. To be honest I like to be capricious sometimes.:) But most part I am faithful, kind and tender person.if you are so serious please contact
